import React from "react"
import classes from './Form.module.css'
const Form = () =>{
    return (
        <section>
            <form>
                <label>Title</label>
                <input type="text"/>
                <label>Opening Text</label>
                <input type="textarea"/>
                <label>Release Date</label>
                <input type="text"/>
                <button className={classes.button}>Add</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    )

}

export default Form
